Class DeployTriggersDatabaseCommand

  • java.lang.Object

    Command, UndoableCommand

    public class DeployTriggersDatabaseCommand
extends DeployDatabaseCommand
    This command looks for a specific database file for deploying a triggers database. This triggers database is considered to be part of the "main" REST API server and content database.
